name: 5 HP
rules: This card starts with 5 HP when defending.

name: Focus
rules: This card requires a Focus roll.

name: Auto
rules: This card's main effect resolves immediately after being revealed in a play or Active Pluck.

name: Max 1
rules: You can only resolve 1 card with this tag per round.

name: Stay
rules: You can keep this card in your play area at the end of a round.

name: Cycle
rules: The effects of this card (limited effects excluded) can be resolved each round.

name: Hit 1
rules: If this card is not defending or has not resolved its main effect, deal 1 damage to a foe. You can't defend with or resolve the main effect of this card for the rest of the round.
